4Geeks Academy offers a Cybersecurity Bootcamp designed for aspiring cybersecurity specialists, requiring no prior knowledge. The bootcamp spans 16 weeks and includes 3 live online classes each week, with a maximum class size of 18 participants. Students gain skills in Windows, Linux, network, and server administration, along with cloud security, penetration testing, and compliance navigation (ISO 27001, NIST). Graduates receive an official 4Geeks Completion Certificate. Classes are available in English and Spanish. For more information, visit: [4Geeks Academy Cybersecurity Bootcamp](https://4geeksacademy.com/us/coding-bootcamps/cybersecurity). stop